  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Teacher manager",
  "description": "<h2>Teaching Manager / Academic Manager</h2><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ol><li><p>Lead and manage the teaching team, including recruitment support, scheduling, performance monitoring, and day-to-day supervision of teachers.</p></li><li><p>Ensure consistent delivery of all academic programmes in accordance with the organisation’s curriculum standards, including regular classes and robotics competition training programmes.</p></li><li><p>Oversee the planning, execution, and quality control of robotics competition programmes, including but not limited to WRO, FLL, NRC, Enjoy AI, and RoboMaster.</p></li><li><p>Conduct regular classroom observations, teaching audits, and performance reviews to maintain high teaching standards and learning outcomes.</p></li><li><p>Plan and implement teacher onboarding, training, and continuous professional development to enhance teaching quality and instructional effectiveness.</p></li><li><p>Monitor student learning progress and competition readiness, and support the resolution of teaching-related feedback or concerns from parents and students.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the Centre Manager and Head Office on academic planning</p></li></ol>",
